    <body>
      <section eId="sec_1428_A">
        <num>1428-A</num>
        <heading>Credit</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_1428_A__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the\ngrantor purchased the property without its being improved by residential\npremises,</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_1428_A__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the grantor improved it by the construction of residential\npremises thereon, and</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_1428_A__subsec_c">
          <num>(c)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the grantor subsequently sold such improved\nproperty. At the time of the first sale of the property after the making\nof the improvement, the grantor shall be allowed a credit equal to the\namount of the tax actually paid on the conveyance immediately prior to\nthe making of the improvement.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
